    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "それって、雑誌のお誕生日企画のアンケートだよね\n『ミラクル☆アイドルバースデー！』、だっけ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the questionnaire for that birthday feature in the magazine‚ right?\n“Miracle☆Idol Birthday!”‚ wasn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、誕生日に合わせて\nやってみたかったことを叶えてくれるみたいなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ they’re supposed to\ngrant you a wish you’ve always wanted to do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょうど今、書き終わったところよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just finished filling it out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4768482048,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_51_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わ～、見てもいい？\nふむふむ、お姉ちゃんのやってみたいことは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~‚ can I see it?\nHmm‚ hmm‚ what you want to do is…",
